\n宜家pick up翻好多之前一齊放棄左既嘢<br />\n令自己好忙冇時間去諗<br />\n<br />\n但其實你話你唔想見我<br />\n我都喺好想同你繼續走落去<br />\n我想講我好愛你<br />\n<br />\n但宜家叫同自己講下嗰會更好<br />\n冇話冇左邊嗰唔得<br />\n但真喺好痛好痛<br />\n做好自己充實自己迎接下一嗰愛自己既人<br />\n唔再愛自己既會成為回憶<br />\n<br />\n分手真喺好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但一齊得既時候又點會諗分開"},{"pid":"5b8378e98209aebc6d4e5e14e012278b3cf322ab","tid":1110911,"uid":190811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4149934f7ef6ab0e8820773b68ffdaf6524347fd","tid":1110911,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T19:01:48.000Z","msg":"出世會死 咁你又出世？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T00:07:15.000Z","msg":"可能我唔想呢"},{"pid":"0adfc7c0f77e2013cbabee43ba88c4460d4676ec","tid":1110911,"uid":41314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T18:05:23.000Z","msg":"好心一早放開我 從頭努力也坎坷<br />\n通通不要好過 來年歲月那麼多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}